isComplex

public boolean isComplex()
Checks if the data of this container is of a complex type.

A complex container holds one or more sub container of type Data as values.

A container is of complex type if getChoiceIndex() returns either Data.Choices.ARRAY, Data.Choices.STRUCTURE or Data.Choices.COMPACT_ARRAY.

Returns:
True if getComplex() may be called without causing an exception.
